        adc-vcc         ( u-channel -- u-value )   with Vcc as reference

        irq-port1       ( -- a-addr ) Memory locations for IRQ-Hooks
        irq-port2
        irq-adc
        irq-timera1
        irq-timera0
        irq-watchdog
        irq-timerb1
        irq-timerb0
        irq-rx
        irq-tx

