High memory access with double address:
       
        x@              ( ud -- u|n ) Fetches from high memory
        x!              ( u|n ud -- ) Stores to high memory

        c@              ( ud -- char ) Fetches byte from high memory
        c!              ( char ud )    Stores byte to high memory


